ibbt.sumo.config
Class OutputDescription

java.lang.Object
  ibbt.sumo.config.OutputDescription

public class OutputDescription
extends java.lang.Object

Class that describes one input dimension This object represents a task for the SampleEvaluator: for each given set of input parameters, the SampleEvaluator has to calculate the output parameters.
